{"tid":2306600,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone防水說明誤導果粉 Apple遭義大利開罰逾3.4億","createTime":"2020-11-30T14:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T16:14:49.000Z","uid":56533,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd344e79ffbeaa9a8d6d82541a737786c0821e8","tid":2306600,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/2ltKfdqzzxVKog66XtEzuZi6kGc=/760x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XBUREX2HEZDQ3H5SQRWLDGQYHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2ltKfdqzzxVKog66XtEzuZi6kGc%3D%2F760x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXBUREX2HEZDQ3H5SQRWLDGQYHM.jpg&h=29cfff1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n義大利反托辣斯監管機關已對美國蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）處以1000萬歐元（約3.47億元台幣）罰款，理由是Apple旗下iPhone防水功能說明不實。<br />\n<br />\n義大利反托辣斯監管機關AGCM今表示，Apple誤導大眾的罪狀有2條。首先，Apple在廣告中宣稱數個iPhone機型（iPhone 8至iPhone 11）在深度介於1至4公尺的水具備防水功能，時間上看30分鐘。不過，AGCM指出，Apple宣稱的防水強度只適用於獲得控制的實驗室環境，現實世界環境不適用。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，AGCM也表示，Apple保固條款誤導大眾。根據Apple免責聲明，如果液體導致手機損壞，手機將不在保固範圍。不過，AGCM指出，Apple也未協助手機因水或其他液體而損壞的的客戶。<br />\n<br />\n義大利2年前也對Apple和三星開罰約1500萬美元，理由是強迫消費者安裝可能導致裝置速度下降或損壞的升級。另外， 法國今年2月以限制電池較舊iPhone作業系統性能為由，對Apple處以2700萬美元罰款。（林文彬／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20201130/GOTSZBRKGNDVDORUREPUAK5QJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20201130%2FGOTSZBRKGNDVDORUREPUAK5QJM%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xD%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=b485f751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20201130%2FGOTSZBRKGNDVDORUREPUAK5QJM%2F&h=0105e631\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20201130/GOTSZBRKGNDVDORUREPUAK5QJM/</a>"},{"pid":"507465fbecd2321c9d511b7b3f278d9ae673f2eb","tid":2306600,"uid":1781,"like":0,"disl